\n+        implicit_keys = send_a_to_b(self.nodes[0], self.nodes[1])\n+\n+        self.sync_all()\n+\n+        check_implicit_transactions(implicit_keys, self.nodes[0])\n+\n+        self.restart_node(0)\n+        self.restart_node(1)",
